org.apache.xpath.compiler

Class PsuedoNames

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.xpath.compiler.PsuedoNames

  • public class PsuedoNames
extends java.lang.Object
    This is used to represent names of nodes that may not be named, like a comment node.
